SELECT COALESCE("t6"."USERID", "t6"."USERID") AS "USERID", "t6"."DISPLAYNAME", "t6"."BADGECOUNT", "t6"."GOLDBADGECOUNT", "t6"."SILVERBADGECOUNT", "t6"."BRONZEBADGECOUNT", "t6"."QUESTIONCOUNT", "t6"."ANSWERCOUNT", "t6"."TOTALSCORE", "t6"."TOTALVIEWS"
FROM (SELECT "Users"."Id" AS "USERID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", CASE WHEN "t4"."BADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."BADGECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "BADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."GOLDBADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."GOLDBADGECOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "GOLDBADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."SILVERBADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."SILVERBADGECOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "SILVERBADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."BRONZEBADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."BRONZEBADGECOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "BRONZEBADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "s1"."QUESTIONCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("s1"."QUESTIONCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", CASE WHEN "s1"."ANSWERCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("s1"."ANSWERCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "ANSWERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "s1"."TOTALSCORE" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("s1"."TOTALSCORE" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALSCORE", CASE WHEN "s1"."TOTALVIEWS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("s1"."TOTALVIEWS" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALVIEWS"
FROM "STACK"."Users"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT ANY_VALUE("Users0"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users0"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", COUNT("Badges"."Id") AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "GOLDBADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "SILVERBADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "BRONZEBADGECOUNT"
FROM "STACK"."Badges"
RIGHT JOIN "STACK"."Users" AS "Users0" ON "Badges"."UserId" = "Users0"."Id"
GROUP BY "Users0"."Id", "Users0"."DisplayName") AS "t4" ON "Users"."Id" = "t4"."USERID"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "Users"."Id" = "s1"."OWNERUSERID"
ORDER BY 9 DESC NULLS FIRST, 3 DESC NULLS FIRST, "Users"."DisplayName"
FETCH NEXT 100 ROWS ONLY) AS "t6"